##################################################################
        CMS Monopole UserCode README file
##################################################################


How to setup this code:
------------------------------------------------------------------
Check out this code from CVS in the src directory of your CMSSW 
release setup ($CMSSW_BASE/src).  Then make a symbolic link to the
Monopole directory under the UserCode directory.
  ln -s UserCode/Monopoles/ 

Now from this top src directory ($CMSSW_BASE/src) one can use 
"scram b" to build the packages.


